"" Do the same to all open buffers
nnoremap <silent> <leader>WW :bufdo let _s=@/<Bar>:%s/\s\+$//e<Bar>:let @/=_s<Bar>:nohl<CR>

"" Reindent Code, strip trailing whitespace and go back to the line the cursor was
